name: Lady Jen Du Plessis, DC
what_you_do: Transforms powerhouse businesses into companies that run smoothly without daily intervention by their leader. Known as The Team Building & Scaling Architect, she has helped over 8,000 entrepreneurs leap from practitioners to thriving enterprises.
who_you_serve: Entrepreneurs and business leaders, with additional focus on mortgage and real estate professionals.
social_proof: Amazon #1 best-selling author, podcaster, TV host, Royal member of the Royal House of Cappadocia and the Royal Order of Constantine the Great and Saint Helen (Dame), helped over 8,000 entrepreneurs.
signature_programs: Conversations to Cash (course), Getting Ready to Hire (course), Business on the Vine (podcast), Mortgage Lending Mastery (podcast), Success to Significance (podcast)
business_focus: Helping entrepreneurs and business leaders scale their businesses and build world-class teams through mentoring, courses, masterminds, and retreats.
service_provided: Group mentoring, private mentoring, online courses, masterminds, retreats, virtual events, in-person events, masterclasses, speaking
